d show its shorter query latency than NSG and HNSW,\nrespectively. Besides, with multicore support, we show that our approach offers\nfaster search latency than highly-optimized GPU implementation and provides\ngood scalability as the increase of the number of hardware resources (e.g., CPU\ncores) and graph sizes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Jan 2022 05:50:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-01"}
