ns of\nwavelengths or greater. By comparing the resulting SEFD formula to the\nSEFD_I^rms approximation, we proved that SEFD_I^rms always underestimates the\nSEFD, which leads to an overestimation of array sensitivity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Jan 2022 07:27:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-04"}
