 geometric features, while the computational efficiency is more than\n100 times higher than that of the full numerical method. Furthermore, it is\nfound that the dynamic trajectories of particles with different geometric\nfeatures are completely different, indicating that the geometric features can\nbe a potential degree of freedom to tune acoustophoretic process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Jan 2022 07:47:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-07"}
